{"title":"献给营林人","authors":["周纲"],"dates":[{"year":1987,"month":11,"day":27}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"献给营林人"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"周纲"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一卷阳光跌碎！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"洒一地"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你的眼睛，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我的眼睛。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"鸟听风吹笛，夜露湿花裙。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"赞美生的开垦。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"满目青山，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"再无攀附的藤，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"拦路的荆；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"再无猥琐的纠缠，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"高大的嫉恨。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"啊，好一群出类拔萃的桦！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"啊，好一群顶天立地的松！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我唤营林人，人在林深处。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"随风传来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"声声“知——了！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山也在和，水也在应……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这是树的语言吗？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一只不会唱歌的鸟，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"落在北纬五十二度弦上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"拨弄生命的竖琴："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我的，我的中国心！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}